node.text:
@yansdining Yan’s Dining, an Authentic Shanghainese Cuisine located at @mandaringallery Mandarin Gallery offers take-out and delivery for their Ala Carte, Dim Sum and Delivery Set Menu now.
.
Featuring the Set Menu A ($118.00) suitable for 4 to 6 pax includes:
▪️Mini Fragrant Pot
▪️Stewing Water Bamboo Shoots with Pork Ribs
▪️Stir-Fried Chinese Cabbage with Mushroom
▪️Tomato Scrambled Eggs
▪️Sesame Chicken Floss Pancake
▪️Steamed Rice
▪️Dessert
▪️*Free Nutritious Soup for Set menu ordered.
.
Visit www.yansdining.sg/order for more info
.
#yansdiningsg #burpple #burpplesg #sgdelivery #sgunited #stayhome #circuitbreakersg
@serenetomato I would love those eggs too minus the tomatoes hahaha!
I spot my fav tomato eggs 😍
Yummm even the rice looks good!
